1. Moji *drugovi* su mi pomogli da završim projekat. (My *friends* helped me finish the project.)
2. *Drugovi*, dobrodošli na sastanak. (Comrades, welcome to the meeting.)
3. Nismo *drugovi* više, raskinuli smo prijateljstvo. (We're not *friends* anymore, we ended our friendship.)
4. Kada smo bili *drugovi* u vojsci, prošli smo kroz mnogo toga zajedno. (When we were *comrades* in the army, we went through a lot together.)
5. *Drugovi*, ne zaboravite da sutra imamo sastanak u 10 sati. (Comrades, don't forget we have a meeting tomorrow at 10 am.)
6. Oni su *drugovi* iz detinjstva, poznajemo se već godinama. (They are *childhood friends*, we've known each other for years.)
7. Naša organizacija okuplja *drugove* koji žele da unaprede društvo. (Our organization gathers *comrades* who want to improve society.)
8. Moja sestra i njeni *drugari* su otišli na izlet u prirodu. (My sister and her *friends* went on a trip to nature.)
9. Zbog loše odluke, *drug* je dobio otkaz na poslu. (Due to a bad decision, *comrade* got fired from his job.)
10. Nismo se svađali, samo smo imali različita mišljenja kao *drugovi*. (We didn't argue, we just had different opinions as *comrades*.)